author: @anaclaudiamaia2911
content: CUFA is a fantastic organization. First was created within the own communities by their members. Second, it’s works direct with the mothers of the families they help through money, food donations, educational projects. The mothers say what they need to support their families. Thank you, Anitta , for supporting CUFA’s work.
